body:
Fixes Pull Request Bug(#3150)

Changes proposed in this pull request:
-
@Override
    public List<String> getChildrenKeys(final String key) {
        return Collections.singletonList(getDirectly(key));
  }
Because Nacos configuration center does not support childrenkeys, you need to configure the schema in the Nacos configuration center in advance, such as: nacosRegistryCenter.persist("/orchestration_ds/config/schema", "sharding_db");

-
@Override
    public boolean tryLock() {
        return true;
    }
Because the Nacos configuration center does not have the concept of lock, the more friendly way is SPI interface.
